  <entry>
    <title>【算法思维札记 - 002】</title>
    <link href="https://erickycooper.github.io/posts/9f2a7c31.html"/>
    <id>https://erickycooper.github.io/posts/9f2a7c31.html</id>
    <published>2026-03-07T22:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2026-03-07T22:00:00.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p><strong>算法思维札记</strong><br>不只讲答案，专讲思路演进与迁移能力</p></blockquote><div class="note info flat"><p><strong>本文定位：</strong> 字符串 + 滑动窗口</p></div><h3 id="题目卡片"><a href="#题目卡片" class="headerlink" title="题目卡片"></a>题目卡片</h3><div class="algo-card algo-code-card">  <ul>    <li><strong>题目：</strong>使二进制字符串变成交替字符串的最少操作次数</li>    <li><strong>难度：</strong>中等</li>    <li><strong>标签：</strong>字符串、滑动窗口、失配计数</li>    <li><strong>题意：</strong>给定二进制串 <code>s</code>，可进行两类操作：<br>      ① 把首字符移到末尾（可做任意次）；<br>      ② 反转任意字符（<code>0 ↔ 1</code>）。<br>      目标是在允许任意次类型 1 的前提下，最小化类型 2 的次数，使字符串变为交替串。    </li>    <li><strong>示例：</strong><br>      输入 <code>s = "111000"</code>，输出 <code>2</code><br>      输入 <code>s = "010"</code>，输出 <code>0</code><br>      输入 <code>s = "1110"</code>，输出 <code>1</code>    </li>  </ul></div><h3 id="核心问题"><a href="#核心问题" class="headerlink" title="核心问题"></a>核心问题</h3><div class="algo-card algo-code-card">  <p>这题本质是：<strong>在所有“旋转后长度为 n 的窗口”里，找与交替模板失配最少的那个窗口</strong>。</p></div><h3 id="第一直觉"><a href="#第一直觉" class="headerlink" title="第一直觉"></a>第一直觉</h3><div class="algo-card algo-code-card">  <p>第一反应是“枚举每一种旋转，再计算改成交替串要翻转多少位”。</p>  <p>但这样会变成 <code>O(n^2)</code>：<code>n</code> 次旋转 × 每次 <code>O(n)</code> 比较，字符串长时会超时。</p></div><h3 id="卡点"><a href="#卡点" class="headerlink" title="卡点"></a>卡点</h3><div class="algo-card algo-code-card">  <p><strong>卡点 1：</strong>旋转是环状结构，直接逐次构造旋转串很重。</p>  <p><strong>卡点 2：</strong>每次都从头统计失配，重复计算太多。</p></div><h3 id="关键思考点"><a href="#关键思考点" class="headerlink" title="关键思考点"></a>关键思考点</h3><div class="algo-card algo-card-highlight algo-code-card">  <ul>    <li>把字符串扩展成 <code>s2 = s + s</code>，这样任意一次“首字符移到末尾”都对应 <code>s2</code> 里的一个长度为 <code>n</code> 的连续窗口；</li>    <li>交替目标只有两种模板：<code>0101...</code> 和 <code>1010...</code>；</li>    <li>用滑动窗口维护当前窗口相对两种模板的失配数 <code>diff1</code>、<code>diff2</code>；</li>    <li>窗口每右移一格，只增量更新进出字符，不重算整段。</li>  </ul>  <p><strong>结论：</strong>遍历所有长度为 <code>n</code> 的窗口，取 <code>min(diff1, diff2)</code> 的最小值即答案。</p></div><h3 id="最终解法（思路）"><a href="#最终解法（思路）" class="headerlink" title="最终解法（思路）"></a>最终解法（思路）</h3><div class="algo-card algo-code-card">  <ol>    <li>设 <code>n = len(s)</code>，构造 <code>s2 = s + s</code>；</li>    <li>遍历 <code>s2</code>，同步统计当前位置对两种交替模板的失配增量；</li>    <li>当窗口长度超过 <code>n</code>，移除左端字符对失配的贡献；</li>    <li>当窗口长度正好为 <code>n</code>，用 <code>min(diff1, diff2)</code> 更新答案。</li>  </ol></div><h3 id="代码（Go）"><a href="#代码（Go）" class="headerlink" title="代码（Go）"></a>代码（Go）</h3><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">func</span> <span class="title">minFlips</span><span class="params">(s <span class="type">string</span>)</span></span> <span class="type">int</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    n := <span class="built_in">len</span>(s)</span><br><span class="line">    s2 := s + s</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    diff1, diff2 := <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">    res := n</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> i := <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; <span class="built_in">len</span>(s2); i++ &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        expected1 := <span class="type">byte</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        expected2 := <span class="type">byte</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;1&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> i%<span class="number">2</span> == <span class="number">1</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            expected1 = <span class="string">&#x27;1&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">            expected2 = <span class="string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> s2[i] != expected1 &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            diff1++</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> s2[i] != expected2 &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            diff2++</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> i &gt;= n &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            j := i - n</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            exp1 := <span class="type">byte</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">            exp2 := <span class="type">byte</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;1&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> j%<span class="number">2</span> == <span class="number">1</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                exp1 = <span class="string">&#x27;1&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">                exp2 = <span class="string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> s2[j] != exp1 &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                diff1--</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> s2[j] != exp2 &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                diff2--</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> i &gt;= n<span class="number">-1</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            res = min(res, min(diff1, diff2))</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> res</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="algo-card algo-code-card">  <p><strong>复杂度：</strong>时间 O(n)，空间 O(n)</p></div><h2 id="思考"><a href="#思考" class="headerlink" title="思考"></a>思考</h2><ol><li>遇到“可旋转/环状”字符串，优先想到 <code>s + s</code> 把环展开成线性窗口。</li><li>遇到“最少修改成某模式”，可先把“修改次数”转为“失配次数”。</li><li>当目标模式数量很少（这里只有两种），可以并行维护多个计数器一次完成。</li></ol><hr><h2 id="本题评分"><a href="#本题评分" class="headerlink" title="本题评分"></a>本题评分</h2><ul><li>思维启发度：⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️</li><li>套路复用度：⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️</li><li>实现复杂度：⭐️⭐️⭐️☆☆</li><li>面试价值：⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️</li></ul><hr><h2 id="一页总结"><a href="#一页总结" class="headerlink" title="一页总结"></a>一页总结</h2><ol><li>旋转不必真的转，<code>s + s</code> + 固定窗口就能覆盖所有情况。</li><li>翻转最少次数 = 与目标模板的最小失配数。</li><li>滑窗增量更新是这题从 <code>O(n^2)</code> 到 <code>O(n)</code> 的关键。</li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
